{
  "stem": "353.3",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Then we were loaded into, again, to a cattle car, and brought to Brinnlitz.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "In Brinnlitz, I said that I'm a electrician, what I was, not knowing nothing.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "But I was.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "So they gave me a job in electric [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "That just means electric factory.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And at then end, in the electric factory, we had a foreman who was German SS-- only one, no more [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Only one.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And he was to give work out.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "You with him, go to this job.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "You're with him.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "You're going to do this.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And [PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] I want to go so fast through Brinnlitz because in Brinnlitz, we had different things too.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "In Brinnlitz, there were a few little boys.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "The-- the commander of the Brinnlitz, his name was Liepold, who was officer of SS.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "He was the commander of the Brinnlitz Schindler factory.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "But [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] he didn't have nothing to say.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "Schindler didn't let him into the factory.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "He had only to stay outside the factory.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "But no Jew went out because everything was inside.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "The factory was inside, the living quarter was inside, so that the-- the-- the Gestapo had nothing to do with us.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "Only Schindler had.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "His orders were order.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "One, I said.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He was only to the electric.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, just in one section.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Because-- because they were bringing the big-- big machines in.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Schindler moved the whole machines from Krakow to Brinnlitz So they were bringing-- Were these electric generators, or-- Everything, everything.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] the Gestapo had nothing to do with-- with the Jews in Schindler.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And he didn't let them do nothing.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They had to only to watch outside that nobody will get away from the-- from the camp.",
      "word_count": 17
    }
  ],
